Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut

Class AcceptanceAtom

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.AcceptanceAtom
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class AcceptanceAtom
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
An AcceptanceAtom is an atomic element in the Boolean condition of a general acceptance condition. An AcceptanceAtom contains
  • a type of acceptance,
  • an ID of an acceptance set, and
  • a Boolean indicating if the acceptance set should be negated.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
